---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Sun Worship — Nazaryah"
  description="From Babel to NASA, the worship of the sun never stopped — it was simply given new names. Trace the thread from ancient altars to modern institutions."
>
  <div class="sw-wrap">

    <!-- ── HERO ── -->
    <section class="sw-hero">
      <p class="sw-label">&#8213; A Critical Examination &#8213;</p>
      <h1 class="sw-title">Sun Worship</h1>
      <p class="sw-sub">
        From Babel to the modern classroom — the oldest religion never stopped.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- ── INTRO ── -->
    <section class="sw-section">
      <div class="sw-prose">
        <p>
          From the moment we say "sunrise" instead of the biblical "dawn," we are speaking the language of a sun-centered world. The sun has been placed at the center of our universe, our calendars, our symbols, and even our religion — from the cross of Tammuz hanging in every church to the Sun-day that replaced the Sabbath of Yahuah.
        </p>
        <p>
          What the ancient world did openly with altars and incense, the modern world does with textbooks, telescopes, and tradition. The worship never stopped — it was simply given new names.
        </p>
        <p>
          This page traces the thread from Babel to NASA, and asks one question: <em>who told you the sun was at the center?</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── CTA BUTTONS ── -->
    <section class="sw-cta-section">
      <p class="sw-cta-label">&#8213; Choose Your Study &#8213;</p>
      <h2 class="sw-cta-title">Where Does the Thread Lead?</h2>
      <p class="sw-cta-sub">
        Four lines of evidence. One ancient lie wearing many masks.
      </p>

      <div class="sw-card-grid">

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-ancient-lie" class="sw-card">
          <span class="sw-card-title">History</span>
          <span class="sw-card-poetic">The Ancient Lie</span>
          <span class="sw-card-body">The historical thread from Babel to Newton — how sun worship migrated from pagan temples into modern textbooks.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/the-priesthood" class="sw-card">
          <span class="sw-card-title">Priesthood</span>
          <span class="sw-card-poetic">Three Branches, One Tree</span>
          <span class="sw-card-body">The three modern institutions — science, the church, and the space agency — that function as the priesthood of the old religion.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/sun-worship/sacred-act" class="sw-card">
          <span class="sw-card-title">Sexual Worship</span>
          <span class="sw-card-poetic">The Sacred Act</span>
          <span class="sw-card-body">Why sun worship and sexual worship were the same religion — and why the obelisk, the dome, and the sun wheel still stand in every capital city.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/holidays" class="sw-card">
          <span class="sw-card-title">Holidays</span>
          <span class="sw-card-poetic">Rituals in Plain Sight</span>
          <span class="sw-card-body">The living rituals of sun worship — the feasts celebrated in every home every year, traced back to their pre-biblical roots.</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── QUOTE ── -->
    <section class="sw-footer-quote">
      <p class="sw-quote-text">"Learn not the way of the heathen, and be not dismayed at the signs of heaven; for the heathen are dismayed at them."</p>
      <p class="sw-quote-ref">— Jeremiah 10:2</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .sw-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0e0904 0%, #1a1208 20%, #160f07 100%);
    color: #f0e0bf;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .sw-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #4a3218;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(180, 100, 20, 0.2), transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0602 0%, #1a1208 100%);
  }

  .sw-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #8a6028;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .sw-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .sw-sub {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    color: #c4a46b;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  .sw-section {
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
  }

  .sw-prose {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #d9c9a8;
  }

  .sw-prose p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .sw-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .sw-prose em { color: #c4a46b; font-style: italic; }

  /* ── CTA SECTION ── */
  .sw-cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2e1f0d;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(100, 60, 20, 0.12), transparent 70%);
  }

  .sw-cta-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #6a4820;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sw-cta-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f0e0bf;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .sw-cta-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #c4ad84;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ── Card grid (new 3-part button format) ── */
  .sw-card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .sw-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: left;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem 1.6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #7a3a14 0%, #5e2a0c 55%, #3d1a08 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(186, 117, 23, 0.35);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.55),
      inset 0 2px 4px rgba(220, 160, 80, 0.25),
      inset 0 -2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .sw-card:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #965a3e 0%, #7a3a14 55%, #5e2a0c 100%);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow:
      0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.65),
      inset 0 2px 4px rgba(220, 170, 100, 0.3),
      inset 0 -2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .sw-card-title {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #fff5e0;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .sw-card-poetic {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #f0d8a4;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .sw-card-body {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #f5e8c8;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER QUOTE ── */
  .sw-footer-quote {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #160f07 0%, #0e0904 100%);
  }

  .sw-quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: #c4a46b;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .sw-quote-ref {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: #5a3e1a;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .sw-card-grid { gap: 1.25rem; }
    .sw-card { padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
    .sw-card-title { font-size: 1.3rem; letter-spacing: 2.5px; }
  }
</style>
